    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb facs="#f0001"/>
                <opener><orgName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/10068294-7">DEPUTATION FOR
                        COMMERCE,<lb/>SHIPPING, AND TRADE</orgName><lb/>
                    <hi rendition="#c"><note type="editorial" place="inline">[date
                            stamp of the
                            <orgName ref="nognd">Administration of Abattoirs and Livestock
                                Markets]</orgName></note>
                    </hi>
                    <dateline>
                        <hi rendition="#right"><placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/tgn/7005289">HAMBURG</placeName>
                            36, <date when="1930-02-04">February 4, 1930.</date></hi>
                    </dateline><lb/>
                    <hi rendition="#right"><placeName ref="geo:53.5517974,9.985772399999973">STADTHAUSBRÜCKE
                        22</placeName>. 8 AM – 4
                        PM<lb/> TELEPHONE: C 4 DAMMTOR 1017</hi><lb/>
                        G.NO.<hi rendition="#i">259</hi><note type="editorial" place="foot">handwritten</note>
                    <gap reason="insignificant"/><lb/></opener>
                <p><hi rendition="#c">The enclosed newspaper clippings are being sent to<lb/> the
                            <orgName ref="nognd">Administration of Abattoirs and Livestock
                            Markets</orgName></hi>
                    for your preliminary
                    attention.</p>
                <p>It might be advisable to resume contact with the practitioners<lb/>
                    of kosher butchering,
                    particularly regarding their acquisition of the<lb/> device tested in <placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/tgn/7011781">London</placeName>.</p>
                <p>The <orgName ref="http://d-nb.info/gnd/10068294-7">Deputation</orgName> also asks
                    for completion of the survey<lb/>
                    of the percentage of Jewish
                    butchering in relation to<lb/>butchering in general.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed><persName ref="nognd">Heidecker</persName></signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
